{"tid":1343981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如光復元朗嗰日去鄉黑啲鋪頭支持下 =_=","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T00:34:55.000Z","uid":91967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3970e97c00fce1982d10af9352cc115c0e31c8b3","tid":1343981,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:03:15.000Z","msg":"Sor用表情撚引你哋入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日嘅仇一定要報，但點報呢？<br />\n<br />\n我地多人，佢地未必夠膽出。<br />\n<br />\n入佢地條村？一來太分散，二來人地地頭好危險，所以唔建議。<br />\n<br />\n所以最好方法，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟上封鎖佢地</span>。一：可以引佢地出黎覆桌、二：可以對佢地有實際影響（佢地最重視錢）。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地唔止嗰日要有行動，仲有日常生活入面都杯葛佢地既鋪頭，個個都可以做！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVjKGn1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVjKGn1.png&h=356b2bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我地而加第一步，係起哂鄉黑既生意既底！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"14a2746940ce9fad8d6194736bba39eb96b2dee9","tid":1343981,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:03:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5e9b7dac4ff2afb9e754ca62ed4062fcdf48442","tid":1343981,"uid":192390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:34:55.000Z","msg":"拆鋪啦 杯你老母  仲想智取牛屎佬？冷氣軍師"}]}